title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-08-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-08-2013 MON






The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 07/08/13

Monday, July 08, 2013 11:34 AM



Glenn and the guys are back from Salt Lake City with a lot to cover,

 including Jim Carrey's "apology" to gun supporters.

 Plus the latest on Middle East,
 including John Kerry off boating while the city of Egypt burns.

 Also, Michael Jackson's secrets are about to be exposed,

 and is a cross on a pitchers mound really THAT offensive?

 Glenn talks about this and the crash in San Francisco over the weekend,

 plus the Lone Ranger doesn't like guns 

   and Luke Skywalker refuses to use his light saber?? 

       And who IS Barack Obama following on Twitter?
